<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>FieldAi Tutorial</title>
  <%- include('../../partials/user/head') %>
  <style>
    .sidebar {
        height: 100vh;
        width: 250px;
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        background-color: #343a40;
        padding-top: 20px;
    }
    .sidebar a {
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 15px 20px;
        display: block;
    }
    .sidebar a:hover {
        background-color: #495057;
    }
    .sidebar a.active {
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: #fff;
    }
    .content {
        margin-left: 250px;
        padding: 20px;
    }
    .carousel-caption {
        background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .carousel-item img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 400px;
        object-fit: cover;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../../partials/user/sidebar') %>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Tutorial</h3>
    <p>Welcome to FieldAi! These tutorials will guide you through the main features of our application.</p>

    <ul class="nav nav-tabs" id="tutorialTabs" role="tablist">
      <li class="nav-item">
        <a class="nav-link active" id="upload-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#upload" role="tab" aria-controls="upload" aria-selected="true">Upload Images</a>
      </li>
      <li class="nav-item">
        <a class="nav-link" id="weather-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#weather" role="tab" aria-controls="weather" aria-selected="false">Weather Data</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <hr>

    <div class="tab-content mt-3" id="tutorialTabsContent">
        <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="upload" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="upload-tab">
            <p>Image Upload and Counting Corn</p>
            <div id="uploadCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                <li data-target="#uploadCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                <li data-target="#uploadCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                <li data-target="#uploadCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
            </ol>
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="/assets/tutorial/upload-step1.jpg" alt="Navigate to Sector">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Step 1: Select Your Sector</h5>
                    <p>Navigate to the dashboard and select the sector where you want to upload images.</p>
                </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/assets/tutorial/upload-step2.jpg" alt="Upload Images">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Step 2: Upload Your Images</h5>
                    <p>Click on "Upload Images" and choose up to the allowed number of images.</p>
                </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/assets/tutorial/upload-step3.jpg" alt="Confirm Upload">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Step 3: Confirm and Submit</h5>
                    <p>Review your selected images and submit the form. Wait for confirmation that the upload was successful.</p>
                </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Carousel Controls -->
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#uploadCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#uploadCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Weather Data Tutorial Tab -->
        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="weather" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="weather-tab">
            <p>Weather Data</p>
            <div id="weatherCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                <li data-target="#weatherCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                <li data-target="#weatherCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                <li data-target="#weatherCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
                <li data-target="#weatherCarousel" data-slide-to="3"></li>
            </ol>
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <!-- Step 1: Overview of the Weather Data Section -->
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="/assets/tutorial/weather-step1.jpg" alt="Weather Data Overview">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Step 1: Weather Data Overview</h5>
                    <p>Learn about the key weather parameters displayed, such as temperature, precipitation, and wind speed.</p>
                </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Step 2: Understanding Heat Accumulation (GDD) -->
                <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/assets/tutorial/weather-step2.jpg" alt="Heat Accumulation">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Step 2: Heat Accumulation (GDD)</h5>
                    <p>Review how Growing Degree Days (GDD) is calculated and why it matters for your crops.</p>
                </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Step 3: Interpreting Precipitation and Wind Data -->
                <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/assets/tutorial/weather-step3.jpg" alt="Precipitation and Wind">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Step 3: Precipitation & Wind</h5>
                    <p>Understand how precipitation and wind speed affect your farming decisions.</p>
                </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Step 4: Farming Tips from Weather Data -->
                <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/assets/tutorial/weather-step4.jpg" alt="Farming Tips">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Step 4: Farming Tips</h5>
                    <p>See how weather data is used to generate actionable farming tips, helping you decide when to plant or irrigate.</p>
                </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Carousel Controls -->
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#weatherCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#weatherCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>

        <hr>
        <div class="text-center">
        <button class="btn btn-success" onclick="window.location.href='/user/dashboard'">Go to Dashboard</button>
        </div>
    </div>

  <footer class="bg-dark text-center text-white py-3 static-bottom">
    <%- include('../../partials/user/footer') %>
  </footer>

  <%- include('../../partials/user/scripts') %>
</body>
</html>
